headline: General Mills (GIS) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: General Mills (GIS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +6.17% and +0.42%, respectively, for the quarter ended August 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
